  "details": "A vulnerability was found in Edimax BR-6428NS 1.10. This issue affects the function formStaDrvSetup of the file /goform/formStaDrvSetup of the component POST Request Handler. Performing a manipulation of the argument stadrv_ssid results in command injection. The attack can be initiated remotely. The exploit has been made public and could be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
